%h4 Complete Catalogue
%ul
  - data.book.editions.each do |edition|
    - if edition.name != "Online"
      - if edition.file_size_mb != nil
        %li= link_to "#{edition.name} (#{edition.file_size_mb} MB)", edition.link
      - else
        %li= link_to "#{edition.name}", edition.link
:markdown
  Each of these alternative formats includes the complete catalogue text,
  all plates and figures, and the regional maps.
%hr
